Class TransitRouterNetworkTravelTimeAndDisutility

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.pt.router.TransitRouterNetworkTravelTimeAndDisutility
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatsimExtensionPoint, TravelTime, TransitTravelDisutility

    public class TransitRouterNetworkTravelTimeAndDisutility
extends Object
implements TravelTime, TransitTravelDisutility
    TravelTime and TravelCost calculator to be used with the transit network used for transit routing. This class is NOT thread-safe!

    mrieser

                                      double time,
                                      Person person,
                                      Vehicle vehicle,
                                      CustomDataManager dataManager)
        Description copied from interface: TransitTravelDisutility
        Returns the disutility to travel on the specified link at the specified time.
        Specified by:
        getLinkTravelDisutility in interface TransitTravelDisutility
        Parameters:
        link - The link for which the travel disutility is calculated.
        time - The departure time (in seconds since 00:00) at the beginning of the link for which the disutility is calculated.
        person - The person that wants to travel along the link. Note that this parameter can be null!
        vehicle - The vehicle with which the person wants to travel along the link. Note that this parameter can be null!
        dataManager - A helper class to enable the cost calculator store arbitrary data during one routing request.
        Returns:
        The disutility to travel over the link link, departing at time time.
